---
---

<section class="light mission" id="mission">
  <div class="wrap section-pad">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="eyebrow reveal">The thesis</div>
      <h2 class="reveal d1">
        The next decade of space will be defined not by what gets launched — but by what gets reused, repositioned, and reached.
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="reveal d2">
        <div class="col-label">Why P78</div>
        <p>
          Stations and constellations need to be serviced. The Moon needs to be worked, not just visited. None of that happens without the vehicles to make it routine.
        </p>
        <p>
          P78 is building that backbone — the connective infrastructure that turns space from a series of one-shot deployments into a working economy reaching all the way to the Moon.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal d3">
        <div class="col-label">What we do</div>
        <div class="caps">
          <div class="cap">
            <span class="num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Connect</h3>
              <p>Move payloads and assets between orbits, on demand.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cap">
            <span class="num">02</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Service</h3>
              <p>Reach, refuel, and reposition what is already in space.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cap">
            <span class="num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Reach</h3>
              <p>Extend routine operations all the way to the lunar surface.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-grid);
    margin-top: var(--space-section-head);
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .mission .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-5);
    }
  }
  .col-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-mono);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--faring-700);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-3);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-light);
  }
  .mission p {
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.35vw, 17px);
    line-height: 1.62;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .caps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule-light);
  }
  .cap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-4) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-light);
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .cap .num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .cap h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(17px, 1.7vw, 21px);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }
  .cap p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--faring-700);
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
